-- Ukraine's Coal Industry Needs Investment for Shale Gas, Izvestia Reports
-- Kateryna Choursina
-- 2010-06-16T05:57:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-16/ukraine-s-coal-industry-needs-investment-for-shale-gas-izvestia-reports.html

          
          
             Ukraine’s coal sector needs
investment in order to develop shale gas deposits and companies
from the U.S. and Europe have expressed interest,  Ekonomicheskie
Izvestia  reported, citing Coal Minister Yuriy Yashchenko.  
 Ukraine’s coal industry does not have the financial
resources to develop shale gas deposits with government backing,
Izvestia quoted Yashchenko as saying.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
